<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mbạrk rbnạ fy̱ kl ḍyq yạ̉ty̱ lnạ bḥbh wywjd ạlṭryq

[V2]
 mbạrk rbnạ fy̱ ktẖrẗ ạlạtẖạm bbrh wrḥmth ybdlhạ bạlslạm

[V3]
 ạldẖy̱ njạnạ whw ynjy̱ wsynjy̱ fy̱ kl ḍyq

[V4]
 2- mbạrk rbnạ ạlmmsk bạlymyn ạltẖạỷl lạ lạ tkẖạf fạ̉nạ ạlmʿyn

[V5]
 fạ̉nạ hw ạlrjạʾ lkl ạlyạỷsyn ạ̹ly̱ yạ kl ạlmtʿbyn

[V6]
 3- mbạrk rbnạ rạʿy̱ ạlkẖrạf ʿly̱ ktfh yḥmlhạ flạ tkẖạf

[V7]
 tdʿh fy̱ wsṭ ạlḍyq fynqdẖhạ wtḥt ạ̉jnḥth ykẖbỷhạ</lyrics>
<title>mbạrk rbnạ</title>
